{"tid":997685,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府派四千元變「一鑊泡」 陳茂波首認「抵鬧」","createTime":"2019-01-27T11:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T11:44:52.000Z","uid":64694,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8480fa07799831b23088cbac3a1b457bfef3c5c2","tid":997685,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.thinkhk.com/d/file/2019-01-27/7ccd9cf67d4532103122845afb4af26d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Fd%2Ffile%2F2019-01-27%2F7ccd9cf67d4532103122845afb4af26d.jpg&h=a334d0e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n財政司長陳茂波在社交網站進行直播，回應市民對財政預算案的訴求，並邀請藝人王祖藍作主持。直播期間網民不斷發「嬲嬲」，陳茂波回應指今次直播「不是為政府死撐，會做好啲」。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波首先就「關愛共享計劃」派發四千元的安排不便致歉，承認是「抵鬧」。<span style=\"color: red;\">他解釋由於本屆政府理財新哲學是要具針對性，因此全民派錢並不合適</span>，而且政府要重新招標設計系統，因此安排需要較長時間。<br />\n<br />\n盈餘少三分二 要想方法令市民受惠<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波又指由於今年財政盈餘較去年少三分二，而且外圍環境不太好，他需要在制訂預算案中考慮有無安排可以令市民受惠。 在回應網民提問時，<span style=\"color: red;\">陳茂波指公屋減租未必是最好利用資源方法，全民免電費亦不環保</span>。<br />\n<br />\n資源上不留難醫管局<br />\n<br />\n另外，陳茂波指他昨日已與食物及衛生局長陳肇始通電話，了解到醫管局醫護人員工作非常辛苦，市民輪候時間亦很長，明白病人家屬會有怨氣。陳茂波強調，一定會向醫管局投放足夠資源，不會留難醫管局 。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-01/27/32634.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2019-01%2F27%2F32634.html&d=ALjBx%2BI5NEGAjTrAc1Fo4gHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=a50cd74b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-01/27/32634.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">笑到仆街，呢樣唔得嗰樣又唔得，乜都唔得，噉佢又想搞啲乜出嚟，佢應該預咗下份財政預算案又俾人插多鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"0db41b36d25d04f8d08d4410088d600954ea4e3a","tid":997685,"uid":64694,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"唔環保，印表格咪重唔環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583bfcc7a663eb7dc51874b5cfcff2174b0b38a2","tid":997685,"uid":182315,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:13:08.000Z","msg":"盈餘比上年少2/3  係因為dom 錢落海?"},{"pid":"c983ce2eb7c5cef20ecf5a27c5ccc03253d5953d","tid":997685,"uid":200641,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"家陣派4000蚊 又唔係派4萬 <br />\n都可以搞埸大龍鳳俾人屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368422870a10f847429ab8fd55b8eb87288d89cb","tid":997685,"uid":4155,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:21:49.000Z","msg":"派四千蚊仲洗得多過派六千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驗腦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64fa2b457ace7d4aa67f5f4b752e17a79487e63","tid":997685,"uid":33497,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:25:04.000Z","msg":"劏房波幾時死全家？"},{"pid":"b43a51f1750a9a860b4cfa369114a8f2e8553c9b","tid":997685,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:44:52.000Z","msg":"印左幾百萬份表格每份幾頁仲連埋信封就好環保？"}]}